{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CRYODEATH</strong>  is a <strong>single-player VR survival horror</strong> game that immerses you in a terrifying <strong>space station</strong> setting, combining <strong>procedural generation</strong>, crafting, and exploration for a truly intense experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You awaken from <strong>cryosleep</strong> aboard the <strong>space station Evriskon</strong>. Your memory is fractured, and the situation is bleak. Your objective: reach the <strong>escape pod</strong> by navigating a procedurally generated labyrinth of dark corridors and haunted rooms, filled with horrifying surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each playthrough offers a unique layout due to the <strong>procedurally generated map</strong>, meaning no walkthrough or strategy guide can fully prepare you. As you explore, you\u2019ll need to gather <strong>tools</strong> and <strong>craft parts</strong> to create gadgets that may help you evade or confront the dangers ahead. Be vigilant\u2014you\u2019re not alone on this station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience true <strong>survival horror</strong> as you adapt to terrifying threats, uncover <strong>hidden secrets</strong>, and fight to survive in a claustrophobic, suspenseful environment. Do you have what it takes to escape?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to test your nerves and courage in <strong>CRYODEATH</strong>\u2014where horror meets <strong>sci-fi</strong>, and every choice matters.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731177723","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205010/page.bg.jpg?t=1731177723","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205010/359939feff74f9b86c25e3d82eaed8a923858607/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731177723","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store